	<p>We recommend the <strong>neural</strong> engine for the most natural Polly speech. Use <code>standard</code> for legacy voices or <code>long-form</code> for extended narration.</p>
	<p><strong>Example voice markup</strong> (with Polly configured as your provider):</p>
	<pre class="code-block" data-lang="xml"><code>&lt;Response&gt;
